00:18:42,478 --> 00:18:44,118
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那我最后问阁下一个问题</font>

275
00:18:44,758 --> 00:18:46,888
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是什么让阁下做出这个决定</font>

276
00:18:49,278 --> 00:18:51,228
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">武者的自尊</font>

277
00:18:52,548 --> 00:18:56,938
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我已年过55 接下来只会逐渐走向衰老</font>

278
00:18:57,098 --> 00:18:59,178
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但现在得到了最佳的机会</font>

279
00:18:59,728 --> 00:19:01,388
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让我们各凭本事</font>

280
00:19:01,628 --> 00:19:03,978
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">决定艾尔孚利登王国的未来吧</font>

281
00:19:04,388 --> 00:19:07,328
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">阁下实在愚蠢之极</font>

282
00:19:07,518 --> 00:19:11,148
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">确实 若非愚蠢又怎能成为一名武者呢</font>

283
00:19:11,618 --> 00:19:14,338
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我会让你见识我的活法</font>

284
00:19:15,608 --> 00:19:17,868
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你确定不是见识你的死法吗</font>

285
00:19:18,218 --> 00:19:23,478
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">两者幷无区别 想活的人会死 想死的人反而能活</font>

286
00:19:23,848 --> 00:19:25,978
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这就是武者</font>

287
00:19:26,308 --> 00:19:29,488
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那就让我踏着你这棵老树前进吧</font>

288
00:19:31,868 --> 00:19:35,708
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">树虽老  但根基依旧坚固</font>

289
00:19:35,898 --> 00:19:37,408
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我已有心理准备</font>

290
00:19:41,038 --> 00:19:44,398
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">凯欧路克·卡迈因还有卡斯德尔·巴卡斯</font>

291
00:19:44,948 --> 00:19:48,248
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">关于交战 我有一个提议</font>

292
00:19:49,638 --> 00:19:55,668
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">想必两位也不想战争旷日持久 祸及无辜百姓</font>

293
00:19:56,378 --> 00:19:58,878
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以我希望定下约定</font>

294
00:19:59,048 --> 00:20:00,478
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一旦我三人被击杀或者俘虏</font>

295
00:20:00,478 --> 00:20:02,778
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其军队马上归入胜者一方</font>

296
00:20:02,958 --> 00:20:03,888
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯</font>

297
00:20:04,758 --> 00:20:10,418
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我明白了 若是我败了 剩下的士兵将直接交由你指挥</font>

298
00:20:13,598 --> 00:20:15,998
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那就先告辞了</font>

299
00:20:17,378 --> 00:20:18,298
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">等等</font>

300
00:20:21,528 --> 00:20:22,818
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">公主殿下</font>

301
00:20:24,838 --> 00:20:26,128
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">卡迈因公爵…</font>

302
00:20:51,658 --> 00:20:53,398
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这就是我的决心</font>

303
00:20:53,738 --> 00:20:55,968
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我将和相马共进退</font>

304
00:20:58,298 --> 00:21:01,268
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你的决心我已经看到了</font>

305
00:21:15,728 --> 00:21:18,918
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉 我没有说服卡斯德尔</font>

306
00:21:20,498 --> 00:21:24,608
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没办法 这是他自己做出的决定</font>

307
00:21:24,868 --> 00:21:27,698
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">沃达公爵 她在您那里吗</font>

308
00:21:27,968 --> 00:21:30,008
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 她在</font>

309
00:21:31,988 --> 00:21:34,268
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">您叫我吗 陛下</font>

310
00:21:36,538 --> 00:21:38,368
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">非常感谢你 茱娜</font>

311
00:21:38,918 --> 00:21:41,008
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">多亏了有你从中牵线</font>

312
00:21:41,168 --> 00:21:43,788
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们才能免于和沃达公爵交手</font>

313
00:21:44,048 --> 00:21:46,778
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我只是遵从了您的命令而已</font>

314
00:21:46,898 --> 00:21:53,388
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">非常抱歉 让我的孙女前来试探陛下是否有为王的资质</font>

315
00:21:55,028 --> 00:21:59,008
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没关系 多亏了您这番举动 我才能和您结盟</font>

316
00:22:01,218 --> 00:22:02,218
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">相马</font>

317
00:22:04,468 --> 00:22:06,868
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们都是你的盟友</font>

318
00:22:09,988 --> 00:22:13,938
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一阵穿梭的疾风 穿越整个世界</font>

319
00:22:14,168 --> 00:22:18,288
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">连接不可能相遇的我们</font>

320
00:22:18,388 --> 00:22:22,418
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">展开没有人看得见的羽翼</font>

321
00:22:22,598 --> 00:22:26,528
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">找寻没有人看得见的奇迹</font>

322
00:22:26,528 --> 00:22:29,838
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">起飞吧</font>

323
00:22:35,428 --> 00:22:39,568
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">继续迷惘明日的方向</font>

324
00:22:39,618 --> 00:22:43,718
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">追求继续选择的勇气</font>

325
00:22:43,858 --> 00:22:47,928
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不曾怀疑天空有多蓝</font>

326
00:22:47,988 --> 00:22:52,388
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">希望我能毫不畏惧世事无常</font>

327
00:22:52,588 --> 00:22:54,808
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">比起将来的梦想</font>

328
00:22:54,808 --> 00:22:56,898
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">超越想象中的未来</font>

329
00:22:56,898 --> 00:23:00,958
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这般时光是如此美好</font>

330
00:23:01,198 --> 00:23:03,258
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我只想徜徉在其中</font>

331
00:23:03,378 --> 00:23:05,428
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和你共同度过现在</font>

332
00:23:05,428 --> 00:23:08,798
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要是能实现就好了</font>

333
00:23:08,798 --> 00:23:13,588
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">穿过湛蓝 绵延不断的天空</font>

334
00:23:13,738 --> 00:23:17,428
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将轮回的命运拉近身边</font>

335
00:23:17,428 --> 00:23:21,848
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">传达思念给紧握的手</font>

336
00:23:21,848 --> 00:23:26,588
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">仅仅希望这就是永远</font>

337
00:23:26,648 --> 00:23:28,638
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">即使现在只是幻影</font>

338
00:23:28,838 --> 00:23:31,028
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就算是在某人的梦境里</font>

339
00:23:31,028 --> 00:23:32,758
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一阵穿梭的疾风</font>

340
00:23:32,758 --> 00:23:37,598
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在抓住它 起飞吧</font>

